      "description": "Hey there, neighbor! I\u2019m finally parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty has been my weekend baby, kept tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and pampered with the best care possible. It\u2019s honestly in such incredible shape that it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014a total dream to drive! There might be a tiny, almost invisible stone chip if you look with a magnifying glass, but to me, she\u2019s absolutely perfect. I\u2019m looking for someone who will love it as much as I have. Come by, have a coffee, and let's get you behind the wheel!",
